<HL>
   International:
   Japan Hopes to Raise Profile of Its Quest
   For Permanent Seat on Security Council
   ----
   By Christopher J. Chipello
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/31/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A10
</SO>
<NS>
UNITED NATIONS (UNN)
</NS>
